    "intro": "In snowy Aspen just before Christmas, Quinn is betrayed on her wedding day when she catches her fiancé cheating with her stepsister. What's worse is that she comes to learn they are also plotting to steal her mother’s diner, which is her one true legacy. In a move of desperation, she hires gentle “hotel waiter” Wesley to pose as her fake boyfriend in an attempt to secure the diner, unaware he is the hidden heir to a luxury hotel empire. A holiday romance built on lies, healing, and true love begins.",
